    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Well-kept car in good overall condition that shows it has been cared for. It presents nicely inside and out, with the kind of light cosmetic wear and minor blemishes you\u2019d expect from a used vehicle, but nothing that takes away from it as a clean, appealing driver. The interior is tidy, the exterior still shows well, and it drives the way a good, solid example should. A buyer should expect a nice, honest car that is ready to enjoy, while still understanding it is not a mint, flawless showpiece.",
      "price": 34900.0,
