    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Needs work and is being sold as a poor-condition driver/project car. This one shows heavy cosmetic wear inside and out, and buyers should expect noticeable age, use, and deferred maintenance throughout. It is not a clean, sorted example, and it will likely need mechanical repairs, reconditioning, and general attention before being considered truly dependable. Best suited for someone looking for a project, a budget fixer-upper, or possibly a parts car depending on their plans. Please come in expecting flaws and needed work, not a turnkey vehicle.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
