      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "A budget-friendly opportunity with plenty of potential, this vehicle offers an accessible entry point for drivers seeking basic transportation or a smart project. It presents as a straightforward, value-focused choice with room for the next owner to make it their own. Priced to reflect its current condition while still delivering real utility, this is an honest offering for someone who recognizes affordable value when they see it.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s priced for someone looking for affordable wheels without a lot of fuss. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but it\u2019s a straightforward, usable vehicle with plenty of potential for a handy buyer, commuter, or anyone needing a cheap runaround. If you know your way around cars or just want something budget-friendly to get started with, this could be a great fit. Sensibly priced and ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with good bones and plenty of usable life left for the next owner. This car shows cosmetic wear and age, but the powertrain pulls through the rev range, the transmission does its job, and it\u2019s the kind of straightforward, mechanical setup that\u2019s easy to live with and maintain. A great option for someone who wants affordable transportation, a shop commuter, or a platform to sort and improve over time. Not a show car, but a capable, honest vehicle with practical value where it counts.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap way into a car. Runs, drives, and gets the job done. Rough around the edges, priced to move fast. Solid deal for the right buyer.",
      "price": 7200.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Turn heads and spark ideas with this honest, full-of-character ride that still brings undeniable presence to the street. It has the kind of well-lived-in charm that makes every drive feel a little more storied, whether you\u2019re looking for a budget-friendly set of wheels, a creative project, or a practical runabout with personality. An ideal opportunity for someone who sees potential, appreciates value, and wants something memorable instead of forgettable.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
